-------Introduction------
This is an JavaFX application to edit text. It has the following major functions:
1. Spell check and correction suggestion. The app can find out misspelled words and suggest most related words to correct them;
2. Word typeahead when inputing;
3. Similar article generation; The app can generator similar articles by training with input text based on Markov chain text model;
4. Score the readability of the input article (Flesch Index);
5. A tool to calculate the word path of morphing from one word into another;

-------Instruction--------
App entrence: application/MainApp

-------Used API-----------
org.fxmisc.richtext
https://github.com/ottypes/rich-text